{"word":"κλείω","slug":"κλείω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰλείω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κλείς\">κλείς</a></el>] ‘close to prevent entry’, <b>lock, shut<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> <a href='B:470 6:6'>Mt 6:6</a>; <a href='B:470 25:10'>25:10</a>; <a href='B:490 11:7'>Lk 11:7</a>; <a href='B:500 20:19'>J 20:19</a>, <a href='B:500 20:26'>26</a>; <a href='B:510 5:23'>Ac 5:23</a>; <a href='B:510 21:30'>21:30</a>; <a href='B:730 20:3'>Rv 20:3</a>; <a href='B:730 21:25'>21:25</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in imagery <b><a href='B:470 23:14'>Mt 23:14</a>; <a href='B:490 4:25'>Lk 4:25</a>; <a href='B:730 3:7'>Rv 3:7f</a>; <a href='B:730 11:6'>11:6</a>.</b> <el>ϰλεῖν τὰ σπλάγχνα <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀπό\">ἀπό</a> τινος</el> = shuts down his heart to someone <b><a href='B:690 3:17'>1 J 3:17</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κλείς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κλέμμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}